Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉清目秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明眸皓齿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一获千金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千客万来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道打架的基本原则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「先下手为强」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够隆重的迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Session #3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(962.667,980)\fad(1500,0)}Honky Tonk Women
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}夜总会女郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有神速枪技与高超牌技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是传说中的女赌客 赌后爱丽丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1325.337,980)}Poker Ailce
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}注：取自伊丽莎白·泰勒主演的电影「扑克俏佳人 Poker Alice」 (1987)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她还活着的话是219岁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 你看上去不像200多岁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且爱丽丝一生未曾输过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠出千却能逢赌必胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎欠了巨额债务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜欢进局子呢 还是来我的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中的启示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理说过「若想洗手 必先动手」 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是想要得到什么就必须先付出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理难道不是让我们放手去赌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当查理·帕卡还会说歌德的格言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛 这只是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的5000五龙和你的梦一起化为了泡影 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里禁止吸烟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别去赌啊 你眼睛太尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赢太多 搞不好会被轰出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你别带我来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝好运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也来玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好牌 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方会来二十一点的赌桌随意输上一局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然你要协助他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 他会把最后留下的一枚筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为庄码交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(933.333,980)}Dealer Chip
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能令你的债务在宇宙中瞬间一笔勾销的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不是运气好 也不是赌技高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我大方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(962,980)}Black Jack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘拜下风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留作纪念了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么大方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么和说好的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一枚筹码应该要交给我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 你出老千我都奉陪了一局呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听到了吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是出老千了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄家在出千？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到我们事务所来一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这里的赌场还兼营健身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该你上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯派克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 总之先逃为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没兑钱呢 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身上果然没有 筹码是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要筹划这场闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你和你们老板都没明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那枚筹码若是落入警察手中就万事皆休了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 还没有找到那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她找出来 出些赏金也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Part B --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我把你们送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢礼为什么是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 果然这位姐姐身上有钱的味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰特 你赢了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说也有二十万吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁让它们化为泡影了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 区区二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我欠的债比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 要讹诈也该有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 那架运输机能卖四十万吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老老实实把筹码交出来不就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筹码？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这东西交给哥顿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少钱他都会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不认识什么叫哥顿的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没打算相信你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 爱因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有在听吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(982,980)}Chip
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是筹码啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1074.667,980)}Chip
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个 这里面藏着微型芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位朋友 赏金头目的情报包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(539.333,980)}AMIGO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 现在是BIG SHOT时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 本周的头号人物是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}交给警察太可惜的她 不可貌相的惯犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 斯派克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫菲·瓦伦丁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏金竟然有600万 物有所值哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杰特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油咯 牛仔们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前头 我可没打算逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空间门的一艘破船上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(774.333,980)}GATE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筹码也在他们手上 所以快一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我们真是没个大人的风范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把年轻小姐关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会在打什么歪主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只是带你去个更舒适的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前才开20万的价 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲·瓦伦丁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我被悬赏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有600万呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 才600万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…欠了多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 求求你们 我不想去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把你交给警察就拿不到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以一直留在同一个地方的 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妈妈的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一族是追寻着爱情 四处流浪的罗姆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1510.333,980)}Romani
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没学问的男人 就是吉普赛人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这种毫无自尊心的外族人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫做Gorgio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}注：罗姆语 指罗姆人以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫我们Gorgio好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在呼唤我 大自然在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和警察说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了 杰特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 我不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少帮我解开一只手啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样连厕所都上不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这女人真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫天上掉馅饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓塞翁失马焉知非福嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理说过 想要得到必须先付出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中得到的启示倒也不是毫无用处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你们是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把筹码还给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对你们只是毫无用处的筹码而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里面的东西似乎能卖高价哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约三年前SIT曾开发过一个解码程序
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为密匙破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1027.67,980)}Crypt Breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成后程序员就被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说程序被卖到了黑市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这程序能解读几乎所有的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并解开防火墙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可谓是把魔法钥匙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个程序本身也加了密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要钥匙来解开它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说警察和ISSP都红着眼拼了命在找这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}注：Inter Solar System Police 太阳系刑警警察机构
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在这里得以拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就在ISSP干些见不得人的买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赌场就算做了巨额交易也不会引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算正好借此瞒过警察的眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的运气不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我们拿着它也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按理应该交给警察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说三亿 三千万如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为魔法钥匙的价钱还算便宜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 600万变成3000万了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「稻秸富翁」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}注：日本童话故事中用一根稻草以物换物最后变成了富翁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这年头还要现金交易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是老派的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自数到三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会断掉手提箱的磁力 让箱子飞到你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你将筹码丢到我们这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认筹码后就连船一起击落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门是用来打开的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Gorgio
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 罗姆人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她逃了 射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰特 准备开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船打下来 你们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她散布了雷达干扰箔条！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用掉它才是正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得像「稻秸富翁」那样从头开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人出千啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- ED：「The Real Folk Blues」--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:53.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛してたと嘆くには
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:58.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あまりにも時は過ぎてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:05.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まだ心のほころびを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:10.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}癒せぬまま　風が吹いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:20.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}乾いた瞳で誰か泣いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:26.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}THE REAL FOLK BLUES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:35.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}本当の悲しみが知りたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:47.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}泥の河に浸かった人生も悪くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:55.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一度きりで終わるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:53.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}想要感慨曾经爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:58.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}岁月却已逝去许久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:05.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}心头伤痕尚未愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:10.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}风儿却已经吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:20.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}谁会用干涸的眼眸为我落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:35.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}但求知晓真正的伤悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:47.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}置身泥沼的人生倒也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:55.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}只要此生何需来世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Next --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.87,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊 这世道真不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萧条得让小孩都忍无可忍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在是看报纸的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bebop船上可是更不太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人不是挺可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.21,0:24:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个 是恐怖分子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.58,0:24:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像打算炸飞木卫三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.58,0:24:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(1150.333,980)}Ganymede
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.27,0:24:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是环境保护团体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 这动物就让他们接收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.39,0:24:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(960,980)}Gateway Shuffle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网关曳步舞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是快忍无可忍了吧


